{"tid":2163782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[泛民入黎] 就算係留 點樣服眾？八號風球腦震盪","createTime":"2020-08-19T00:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T06:40:34.000Z","uid":1591,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f73aed247d9f1bb3e3b1cc7044d7aa1809a5c7f3","tid":2163782,"uid":1591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T00:37:34.000Z","msg":"其實泛民現任議員大致分為呢兩批<br />\n1. 原本話退休者(張超雄梁耀忠莫乃光等)<br />\n2. 競逐連任但初選後落敗者(黃碧雲郭家麒等)<br />\n3. 初選勝出者(譚文豪許志勇等)<br />\n方案如下<br />\n3. 就算選舉如常 都好大可能成功連任 民意mandate應問題不大 重點應在說服市民 <br />\n如一年工作如何比總辭有效 但忌口號式「阻止惡法blablabla」<br />\n1.&amp;2.未來一年都係bonus黎 理應將一部分資源(不論薪津、助理名額、實報實銷開支)<br />\n最起碼分一部分出黎予公民社會<br />\n如果更進一步 能夠突破派系之爭 提名抗爭派為其助理(影子議員)更佳<br />\n<br />\n 集思廣益 大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f130e0205fcfe015edf92048c2fa30e6acb025c1","tid":2163782,"uid":1591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T00:55:57.000Z","msg":"612 721 831 101 104 1111"},{"pid":"96e875323edd87e21453458b50d0e70602e97d7c","tid":2163782,"uid":1591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"612 721 831 101 104 1111<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2138feca4f03e4a3786f32041855022b1a9a1501","tid":2163782,"uid":1591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T02:52:04.000Z","msg":"612 721 831 101 104 1111<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba1163ecb8322674206a3b7be72cf81877226b7","tid":2163782,"uid":1591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"612 721 831 101 104 1111<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgm